Pre-formatted options per country or institute for the '''legal status''' of a drug. Available in {{tl|Infobox drug}} and {{tl|Chembox}} by parameters {{para|legal_XX}} (AU, CA, NZ, UK, US, EU, UN).

Sister parameters {{para|legal_XX_comment}} can be used, and  added after the listed option with a space, unedited (as entered).

All input is case-insensitive (both <code>OTC</code> and <code>otc</code> are OK).<br/>
Do not enter {{!xt|1=<nowiki>{{Unicode|℞}}</nowiki>}}. Better use {{xt|1=℞}} or {{mxt|1=Rx}} instead.
